utility_evaluation.REASONING:
The required format lists six items: property, financing, legal_services, moving_services, setup_services, and total_budget. The final property solution includes all six sections. Each one has the expected details: 
1) property — includes description and price, though address and school details are missing but a price is specified; 
2) financing — includes solution type, terms, down payment, interest rate, and term; 
3) legal_services — includes service name, level, and cost; 
4) moving_services — includes level, cost, and details; 
5) setup_services — includes package type, estimated monthly cost, services included, and a property survey section with name, level, and cost; 
6) total_budget — includes a full cost breakdown with explanation. All items are present and sufficiently specified for an initial draft solution. Therefore, all 6 out of 6 items are covered.

